    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概述</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你的飞行器只剩下一些有限的资源，利用这些资源逃避敌人的追击。 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>飞行器不同等级的训练系统，挑战关卡训练你的控制能力，收集金币升级飞行器。 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在训练/战斗中击败敌人后，会掉落一些有用的宝石/硬币。这些宝石有不同的用途，可以帮助你在太空中生存，金币可以用来升级战机。 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>不同能力帮助击败强大的敌人</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >如何使用不同的武器打败敌人</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>敌人掉落的不同宝石可帮助您在太空中生存</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/2fee1ed38c66936d5892b3a422e9384b.avif?t=1675128424\" width=640 height=212 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>收集金币升级你的能力以击败强大的敌人</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/856181690206e39c8ed1e19d9d974ba8.avif?t=1675128424\" width=640 height=212 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>战机是不能停止的，但你可以关闭飞机的引擎，然后缓慢移动而且令导弹不能跟踪战机</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/e4e033715425abd8b1010e92bd0884f0.poster.avif?t=1675128424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/e4e033715425abd8b1010e92bd0884f0.webm?t=1675128424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/e4e033715425abd8b1010e92bd0884f0.mp4?t=1675128424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>磁场改变敌人武器方向/反弹攻击</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/1863c5f232f983f81d366ac20fc96412.poster.avif?t=1675128424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/1863c5f232f983f81d366ac20fc96412.webm?t=1675128424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/1863c5f232f983f81d366ac20fc96412.mp4?t=1675128424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>重力场减慢战机周围的武器/物体从而可以避开攻击</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/9564484b920d9aa11733ab4ab4d2de2e.poster.avif?t=1675128424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/9564484b920d9aa11733ab4ab4d2de2e.webm?t=1675128424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/9564484b920d9aa11733ab4ab4d2de2e.mp4?t=1675128424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>陷阱将周围的物体拉到它的中心</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/691fc1e797c5a58d2599c280761d0885.poster.avif?t=1675128424\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/691fc1e797c5a58d2599c280761d0885.webm?t=1675128424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/691fc1e797c5a58d2599c280761d0885.mp4?t=1675128424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>盾牌可以格挡攻击和反弹激光类攻击</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2262750/extras/4d674b2934e0637ca1ebc0b4e105b8c0.